snippet.title: Ratchanok Intanon รัชนก อินทนนท์ - Queen of Comebacks
snippet.description:
Ratchanok Intanon is the first badminton player from Thailand to achieve the World no 1 ranking in singles in badminton. She also holds the record for being the youngest World Champion ever, at just 18 years old. She started from a very modest background,  both her parents were workers at the Banthongyord sweet factory. Her calm and humble character, and beautiful playing style have won the hearts of many badminton fans around the world. 
❤️
